# TODO(plan3-infra): These are PLACEHOLDER files for cargo check / scaffold.
# The real node binaries are NOT committed — they are downloaded by the CI
# packaging pipeline per target triple (see docs/architecture/2026-06-24-host-bridge-plan3-infra-todos.md).
#
# Format: node-<target-triple>  (Tauri externalBin convention)
# e.g.:  node-aarch64-apple-darwin
#         node-x86_64-apple-darwin
#         node-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc
#         node-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu
#
# The pipeline fetches each from https://nodejs.org/dist/<version>/ and renames it.
node-*
